### CREATE CLIENT EXAMPLE
POST http://localhost:8080/api/clients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nom":"Client Test",
  "email":"client@test.com",
  "telephone":"0600000000",
  "adresse":"Casablanca"
}

###

### CREATE ARTICLE EXAMPLE
POST http://localhost:8080/api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nom":"Article Test",
  "prix":100,
  "quantite":10
}